com.i2group.apollo.useractivitylogger

Class NoOpUserActivityLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.useractivitylogger.NoOpUserActivityLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUserActivityLogger

    public final class NoOpUserActivityLogger
extends Object
implements IUserActivityLogger
    A trivial implementation of IUserActivityLogger that performs no logging. When logging is not required, this is an efficient option.
